  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to determine the precision of an unobtrusive sleep measurement
      system. The system measures a force sensor signal under the mattress and analyzes sleep
      quality. The system measures: time in bed, sleep stages, sleep fragmentation, heart rate,
      respiration rate, sleep related breathing disorders, and limb movements.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
